{"tid":1406890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽朝地鐵站就算罷唔罷到工嘅人都要幫手！好簡單！","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T18:41:36.000Z","uid":238467,"like":126,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"5f54c488b72c2f58525b22fb6655a51290e679af","tid":1406890,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:21:33.000Z","msg":"就係幫不合作運動前線手足打氣！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTuApPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTuApPY.png&h=c68b9cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我完全明白有好多人同手足無辦法咁方便罷工<br />\n而唔洗擔心 我地係會幫你地罷嘅！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但係我地做緊野嘅同時<br />\n係需要有人做以下幾樣重要嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一 好似上次嘅不合作運動咁<br />\n一定會有人話我地係做緊同民意相反嘅事<br />\n請各位打工仔同手足請唔好吝嗇你地嘅掌聲同歡呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁班藍絲奴工就會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二 各位手足 請保持冷靜<br />\n我地做自己野就得 必要時 問下現場有無人支持<br />\n到時就會有第一點嘅人幫手<br />\n盡量避免直接開佢波<br />\n人地開我地波嘅話 咁就識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三 唔係前線嘅手足<br />\n做文宣！！！ 可以大聲播鏗鏘集<br />\n可以大聲播立場 乜都得<br />\n強迫佢地睇 脫離TVB嘅魔爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 叫大家罷工去七區集會<br />\n返屋企換套衫好 直接去又好<br />\n基本上有齊不反對通知書<br />\n和理非同伴請放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！！！！！<br />\n缺一不何！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫我推下<br />\n聽日就係喇 想集中下意見<br />\n大家有意見都可以提出討論 <br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EW1V78v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEW1V78v.png&h=f3be1ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0297fdb9fbf5d93b8b4410db5ac70f0f0523600","tid":1406890,"uid":180485,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"大西北既牛牛全部同我入哂黎！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花］8月5朝早7點15元朗西鐵站要屯元天人！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391481</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxBTJS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxBTJS.png&h=ded34d59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EcETVXc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcETVXc.png&h=1d434fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvQDnCd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvQDnCd.png&h=cbd48ad4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"628460f341ffbcf7ba4a6af7f987530d75ad6f94","tid":1406890,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"我知依家出面好多事發生緊<br />\n但都想手足討論下聽朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊係七點左右嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90dfa296243144fe839763bf7919da2d51e3f3e","tid":1406890,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl