/>\n缺一不何！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫我推下<br />\n聽日就係喇 想集中下意見<br />\n大家有意見都可以提出討論 <br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EW1V78v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEW1V78v.png&h=f3be1ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"聽日越早不合作越好 公司出哂聲要7:30番工 相信好多人都好早出門"},{"pid":"8dd1eec410fc56167f66afa3bfad011672ca43e4","tid":1406890,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"幫手推 好驚聽日又把握唔到機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e32699e451798fad58e3a2ab51a31c8c1fa9f4","tid":1406890,"uid":265058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"巴士無人講？"},{"pid":"3b69923849b12258bf7fdb684c8fb07789baf221","tid":1406890,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25e32699e451798fad58e3a2ab51a31c8c1fa9f4","tid":1406890,"uid":265058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"巴士無人講？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"巴士嗰啲同地鐵處理手法唔同<br />\n我跟上次嘅經驗諗以上嘅方法<br />\n巴打有無對巴士嘅見解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68d173b1831dd2d